Name: Email
Description: The electronic address type defined as an electronic mail (e-mail) address consisting of a username, the @ sign, and a mail domain name.

Name: Internet
Description: The electronic address type defined as an interconnected system of networks that connects computers around the world via the TCP/IP protocol.

Name: Intranet
Description: The electronic address type defined as a privately maintained computer network that can be accessed only by authorized persons, especially members or employees of the organization that owns it.
